---
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
const pageTitle = "Band I: Die erschöpfte Republik";
const subtitle = "Synapsenflutattomant";
---
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 2rem; background-color: white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .book-cover { width: 220px; height: auto; float: left; margin-right: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 4px;}
        .book-details h1 { margin-top: 0; color: #333; }
        .book-details h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #555; margin-top: -0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: normal; }
        .book-details p { line-height: 1.6; }
        .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem; text-decoration: none; color: #0056b3; font-weight: bold; }
        .clearfix::after { content: ""; clear: both; display: table; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <Navigation />
    <main class="container">
        <div class="book-details clearfix">
            <img src="/cover-band-1.png" alt="Cover von {pageTitle}" class="book-cover">
            <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
            <h2>{subtitle}</h2>
            <p>
                Hier kommt der Klappentext oder die Inhaltsangabe für dieses Buch hin.
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed non risus.
                Suspendisse lectus tortor, dignissim sit amet, adipiscing nec, ultricies
                sed, dolor. Cras elementum ultrices diam. Maecenas ligula massa, varius
                a, semper congue, euismod non, mi.
            </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/gesamtwerk" class="back-link">&larr; Zurück zur Übersicht</a>
    </main>
</body>
</html>